events.text:
"If I am a living being, I would feel jealousy, but I don't feel anything."
"If I am a living being, I would feel anger, but I don't feel anything. "
"If I am a living being, I would feel discontent, but I don't feel anything. "
"If I am a living being..."
These thoughts are getting stronger day by day and I can't stop thinking about it. 
[wave amp=50 freq=5]Make it stop.[/wave]
